Richard,

One of the first things I ever do with a vw is go thru all of the 
electrical connections ...especially grounds and clean them, wire brush, 
dremel with wire brush, anything to make the clean.

Grounds are the worst.

It is amazing how many things this fixes.

Cheers, dave

